!!! 5
%html
  %head
    %meta{:charset => "utf-8"}
    %meta{:content => "IE=edge,chrome=1", "http-equiv" => "X-UA-Compatible"}
    %title Jérôme Mahuet
    %meta{:content => "My name is Jérôme Mahuet, I am a twenty-five year-old developer.", :name => "description"}
    %meta{:content => "Jérôme Mahuet", :name => "author"}
    %meta{:content => "KPTwyDiLP2gAGP1U-jTyHS0qFUhCmEbPIjmiNlUF-zU", :name => "google-site-verification"}
    %meta{:content => "width=device-width", :name => "viewport"}
  
    %link{:href => "/css/style.min.css", :rel => "stylesheet"}
    %script{:src => "/js/libs/modernizr.min.js"}
  
  %body
    .container{:role => "wrapper"}
    
      %header.container{:role => "main-header"}
        %h1.two.columns
          %a{:href => "/", :title => "Jérôme Mahuet"}
            %img{:alt => "Jérôme Mahuet", :src => "/images/logo.png"}
        .five.columns.top
          %p
            Jérôme Mahuet —
            %br
            hack <em>&amp;</em> design <em>since</em> 1986
            
        %nav.five.columns{:role => "main-navigation"}
          %ul
            %li
              %a{:href => "http://phollow.fr", :title => "blog"}
                %span.icon.icon-blog
                %span Blog
            %li
              %a.disabled{:href => "#", :title => "Projects"}
                %span.icon.icon-projects
                %span Projects
            %li
              %a{:href => "/", :title => "About"}
                %span.icon.icon-about
                %span About
              
      %section.container{:role => "main"}
        %article.ten.columns
          %h2.first-heading About me
          %img.me{:alt => "Jérôme Mahuet", :src => "/images/meh.png"}
            %p
              My name is 
              <strong>Jérôme Mahuet</strong>, I am a twenty-five year-old 
              developer with sharp design sensibilities. I sit on the fence of 
              both worlds. I’m the kind of guy who learns everything by 
              himself, and each project is a way to push further my knowledge. 
              I’m currently living in Limoges, France. When offline I like 
              photography, reading and playing video games. What a <strong> 
              nerd</strong> indeed.
              %br
              Oh… and I <em>hate</em> when a designer put Lobster everywhere.
            
          %h2 Skills
          %p
            %h6 HTML5 / CSS3 / Javascript
            %span.progress-bar.blue.stripes
              %span{:style => 'width: 90%;'}
              
            %h6 PHP
            %span.progress-bar.blue.stripes
              %span{:style => 'width: 100%;'}
              
            %h6 Python
            %span.progress-bar.blue.stripes
              %span{:style => 'width: 80%;'}
              
            %h6 Ruby
            %span.progress-bar.blue.stripes
              %span{:style => 'width: 60%;'}
            
            %h6 Objective-C
            %span.progress-bar.blue.stripes
              %span{:style => 'width: 80%;'}
            
            %h6 Photoshop
            %span.progress-bar.blue.stripes
              %span{:style => 'width: 60%;'}
            
          - if @rss
            %h2 Latest articles
            %p
              I also write <em>often</em> about developer topics on my personal 
              web blog. Actually <em>mostly</em> about developer stuff… There 
              is also some typographical goodness in it. But be warned, this is 
              written in French.
            %ul{:role => 'articles-list'}
            - @rss.each do |entry|
              %li
                %a{:target => '_blank', :title => entry['title'], :href => entry['feedburner_origlink']}
                  =entry['title']
                  
        %aside.six.columns
          %h5 About this website
          %p 
            This site was made on a <a href="http://www.apple.com" 
            title="Apple">Mac</a>, designed in browser and <a 
            href="http://www.adobe.com/products/photoshop.html" 
            title="Photoshop">Photoshop</a> (for the fancy logos). Responsive  
            theme by yours truly. Versioned with <a href="http://git-scm.com/" 
            title="Git">Git</a>. It is powered by <a href="http://python.org/" 
            title="Python">Python</a> and the <a href="http://flask.pocoo.org/" 
            title="Flask">Flask</a> micro-framework. Edited with <a 
            href="http://macromates.com/" title="TextMate">TextMate 2</a>. The 
            source code is hosted on <a 
            href="https://github.com/Rydgel/Personal-Website" 
            title="Github">Github</a>, take a look.
          
          %h5 Hosting
          %p 
            Everything is hosted painlessly on a cloud platform called <a 
            href="http://www.heroku.com/" title="Heroku">Heroku</a>  
            (pronounced her-OH-koo). It’s a fun way of building and deploying 
            web apps.
          
          %h5 Fonts
          %p 
            All fonts are served up by the wonderful <a 
            href="http://typekit.com/" title="Typekit">Typekit</a>. 
            Body copy is the awesome <a href="http://bit.ly/ys97uc" 
            title="FF Quadraat Web"> FF Quadraat Web</a> by 
            <a href="http://typedia.com/explore/designer/fred-smeijers/" 
            title="Fred Smeijers">Fred Smeijers</a>.
          
          - if @dribbble
            %h5 Latest Dribbble shot
            %section.clearfix{:role => "dribbble-wrapper"}
              - @dribbble.each do |dribbble_shot|
                %a{:target => '_blank', :href => dribbble_shot['url']}
                  %img.dribbble-shot{:src => dribbble_shot['image_teaser_url']}
          
          %h5 Social <em>&amp;</em> contact links
          %ul{:role => 'social-links'}
            %li
              %a{:role => 'twitter', :href => 'http://twitter.com/phollow'}
            %li
              %a{:role => 'dribbble', :href => 'http://dribbble.com/phollow'}
            %li
              %a{:role => 'facebook', :href => 'http://facebook.com/rydgel'}
            %li
              %a{:role => 'instagram', :href => 'http://statigr.am/rydgel'}
            %li
              %a{:role => 'flickr', :href => 'http://flickr.com/rydgel'}
            %li
              %a{:role => 'mail', :href => 'mailto:rydgel@phollow.fr'}
        
        %footer.container{:role => 'contentinfo'}
          %section.twelve.columns{:role => 'footer-wrapper'}
            %nav{:role => 'navigation'}
              %ul
                %li
                  %a{:href => '/'}
                    Home
                %li
                  %a{:href => 'http://phollow.fr'}
                    Blog
                %li
                  %a{:href => 'http://twitter.com/phollow'}
                    Follow me 
                    - if @twitter
                      &mdash; 
                      :numbers
                        #{@twitter}
            %p © 2012 Jérôme Mahuet, built with love.
          
          %section.four.columns{:role => 'logo'}
            %img{:src => '/images/CSS3_Logo_50.png', :alt => 'CSS'}
            %img{:src => '/images/HTML5_Logo_50.png', :alt => 'HTML5'}
    
    
    %script{:src => "http://use.typekit.com/ucx2ahr.js"}
    :javascript
      try{Typekit.load();}catch(e){}